    <td colspan="2"><p data-start="1996" data-end="2330"><strong data-start="1996" data-end="2041">The Zen Bloks® Leg Elevation Wedge Pillow</strong> is engineered for steady, structured elevation that guides your lower body into a natural, centered position. Its wide platform and ergonomic leg-wedge geometry support consistent alignment, eliminating the shifting and collapsing feel of stacked pillows or low-density foam alternatives.</p>
<p data-start="2332" data-end="2726">Built with high-density performance foam, this elevation pillow maintains its form with repeated use, creating a smooth, stable surface for daily recovery habits, evening reset routines, or moments when long periods of sitting or standing leave your legs feeling overworked. The balanced incline and repeatable structure help both legs settle into a dependable position without readjusting.</p>
<p data-start="2728" data-end="3060">Each wedge includes a breathable, removable cover and is available in multiple incline heights to match different body proportions and comfort preferences. Designed for use on mattresses, sofas, or floor setups, this leg support pillow provides a reliable, alignment-focused foundation for structured rest and lower-body relaxation.</p></td>
